This paper proposes a modification to deep learning architectures to improve transparency and interpretability of classification decisions. The paper draws on ideas from nonparametric kernel regression and conformal methods. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
